# teaser: Write a product review
- id: 1558-write-an-product-review-for-affiliate-blog
  title: Write an Product Review for Affiliate Blog
  tags:
  - writing
  - write
  - product
  - review
  - affiliate
  - blog
  family: writing
  body: Read and write an SEO-optimized product review as per the mentioned below
    the Product Description. Review must be 100% unique and attractive. Write a completely
    informative review that is useful for readers. Use various sentences and use the
    words "If you're", "Are you", "Do you" and "Have you" at the beginning of some
    sentences randomly. Use active voice maximum and tune should be friendly. Write
    the review 150 words long within 3 paragraphs. Write as a 3rd person. Write it
    in [TARGETLANGUAGE]. [PROMPT]
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
